      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. It\u2019s been babied since the day I got it and is in truly pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did when it first left the lot! Not a scratch or a smudge to be found. I\u2019m looking for a friendly new owner who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out and come see this beauty for yourself! \u2728",
