    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a superlative example of the S54-powered era. This 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been recently overhauled to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis is structurally impeccable, with the rear subframe mounting points inspected and reinforced to prevent fatigue. Every suspension bushing and damper retains factory-spec rebound and compression characteristics, offering the communicative steering and tactile feedback expected of a preserved specimen. Finished in concours-level paint with a flawlessly maintained interior, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
