    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that remains in flawless, showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, and has been treated with a multi-year ceramic coating. The original alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather seats maintain their original matte factory finish with no bolstering wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. All onboard electronics, climate controls, and driver-assist features operate perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians at the dealership. I possess the full service binder, original window sticker, and both key fobs. To provide absolute peace of mind given my growing seller profile, I am more than happy to facilitate a pre-purchase inspection at a local shop of your choice.",
